#. <section class="sutta" id="an1.248-257"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.248-257:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:0.2"
msgid "19. Chaṭṭhavagga"
msgstr "19. Sixth"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:0.3"
msgid "248–​257"
msgstr "248–​257"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.26"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: tapussabhallikā → tapassubhallikā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an1.248-257:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ upāsakānaṃ paṭhamaṃ saraṇaṃ "
"gacchantānaṃ yadidaṃ tapussabhallikā vāṇijā. (1)"
msgstr ""
"“The foremost of my laymen in first going for refuge are the merchants "
"Tapussa and Bhallika."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:2.1"
msgid "… Dāyakānaṃ yadidaṃ sudatto gahapati anāthapiṇḍiko. (2)"
msgstr "… as a donor is the householder Sudatta Anāthapiṇḍika."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:3.1"
msgid "… Dhammakathikānaṃ yadidaṃ citto gahapati macchikāsaṇḍiko. (3)"
msgstr "… who speak on the teaching is the householder Citta Macchikāsaṇḍika."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:4.1"
msgid ""
"… Catūhi saṅgahavatthūhi parisaṃ saṅgaṇhantānaṃ yadidaṃ hatthako āḷavako. (4)"
msgstr ""
"… who attract a following by the four ways of being inclusive is Hatthaka "
"Āḷavaka."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:5.1"
msgid "… Paṇītadāyakānaṃ yadidaṃ mahānāmo sakko. (5)"
msgstr "… who donate good things is Mahānāma Sakka."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:6.1"
msgid "… Manāpadāyakānaṃ yadidaṃ uggo gahapati vesāliko. (6)"
msgstr "… who donate nice things is the householder Ugga of Vesālī."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:7.1"
msgid "… Saṅghupaṭṭhākānaṃ yadidaṃ hatthigāmako uggato gahapati. (7)"
msgstr "… who attend on the Saṅgha is the householder Uggata of Hatthi Village."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
#. VAR: sūrambaṭṭho → sūro ambaṭṭho (bj, s1-3, km, pts1) | surabandho (mr)
msgctxt "an1.248-257:8.1"
msgid "… Aveccappasannānaṃ yadidaṃ sūrambaṭṭho. (8)"
msgstr "… who have experiential confidence is Sūrambaṭṭha."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:9.1"
msgid "… Puggalappasannānaṃ yadidaṃ jīvako komārabhacco. (9)"
msgstr "… who have confidence in a person is Jīvaka Komārabhacca."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an1.248-257:10.1"
msgid "… Vissāsakānaṃ yadidaṃ nakulapitā gahapatī”ti. (10)"
msgstr "… who are intimate is the householder Nakula’s father.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.248-257:10.2"
msgid "Vaggo chaṭṭho."
msgstr ""
